I just love lists, don't you? The way you can think you're almost done, only to discover there are more pages than you thought? Warms my heart.

Okay! I need you to go kill some {@LinkCreature:38#12#gluttonous fangspawns}. That'd be pretty swell of you.

Check in with Elmaire at Craterview Outpost in Sienna Canyon when you've handled that.

Good job. Here's your reward.

Keep up the good work!
